# Persistent Memory

Use this vault as shared cross-tool memory.

Run when context is needed:

```bash
node "$CKW_KIT_ROOT/scripts/session-start.mjs"
node "$CKW_KIT_ROOT/scripts/memory-inject.mjs" "<prompt>"
```

Validate Markdown writes:

```bash
node "$CKW_KIT_ROOT/scripts/validate-write.mjs" "<changed-file.md>"
```

Shared memory lives in `99_系统/记忆/`. Active work state lives in `_state/`.
